description: The construction of two part 4/part 5/part 6/part 7 storey buildings (Blocks A & B) and one part 5/part 7/part 8 storey building (Block C) containing 132 dwellings, comprising 13 studios, 63 one bedroom, 47 two bedroom and 9 three bedroom self-contained flats, together with associated landscaping, provision of plant, refuse stores and 154 cycle spaces on the Venson Site, Conington Road SE13 .
